name: New: Smoothie Breakfast Bundle
description: Kick off your day with delicious smoothies rich in fibre! This bundle contains two of each of our 3 breakfast smoothies:2 x Berry Breakfast - Banana, Blueberry, Raspberry, Gluten Free Oats

name: New: Smoothie Flavour Blast Bundle (Pack of 12)
description: Our new sampling of Springtime flavours. This bundle contains two packs of each smoothie:2 x Raspberry Rhubarb - Apple, Rhubarb, Pomegranate, Raspberries

name: Smoothie Taster Bundle (Pack of 12)
description: The best way to find your favourite! This bundle contains two servings of our 6 best-selling smoothies:2 x Dragonfruit - Banana, Mango, Purple Dragon Fruit 2 x Lean Green - Apple, Pear, Spinach, Carrot, Ginger 2 x Orange Energizer - Mandarin, Mango, Carrot, Turmeric, Ginger 2 x Coconut Cooler - Mango, Pineapple, Banana, Coconut 2 x Berry Blast - Banana, Strawberry, Blueberry, Flax 2 x Berry Breakfast - Banana, Blueberry, Raspberry, Gluten Free Oats

name: Mango Lime Smoothie (Pack of 5)
description: A golden blend that tastes as vibrant as it looks. A twist of lime brings the tropical fruit flavours in this smoothie to life: succulent mango, exotic papaya, sweet pineapple.

name: Watermelon Chia Smoothie (Pack of 5)
description: Summer's ultimate thirst-quencher. Juicy watermelon, sweet strawberry and smooth banana blitz with zingy lime and filling chia seeds to make a bright breakfast or post-workout refresher.

name: Strawberry Goji Smoothie (Pack of 5)
description: Pink power! Sweet strawberry and creamy banana join sour cherries and tart red goji berries in this vitamin C-packed smoothie. Papaya lends a gentle exotic fruitiness.
